{"tid":435604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"彭定康稱已去信林鄭　關注不排除往後禁其入境說法","createTime":"2017-10-14T12:09:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T17:04:58.000Z","uid":39464,"like":65,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"d1b6f1d856090543a705a2337c597797706a954b","tid":435604,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T12:09:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171014/s00001/04ddfd25bd0d58e65ce20cdb52c9b4c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171014%2Fs00001%2F04ddfd25bd0d58e65ce20cdb52c9b4c4.jpg&h=897dc27f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國保守黨人權委員會副主席羅哲斯（Benedict Rogers）周三（11日）被拒入境香港，特首林鄭月娥前天被問到，往後會否有可能拒絕前港督彭定康入境時，稱不能排除任何可能。彭定康關注有關言論，他向英國《衛報》表示已去信林鄭月娥並正等候回覆。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥昨出席電台節目時表示，表示不會評論個別個案，但指一旦情况被視為外交事務，就會由中央政府負責。被問到會否有可能拒絕前港督彭定康入境，林鄭稱不能排除任何可能。<br />\n被點名的彭定康向英國《衛報》表示，就此說法已去信林鄭月娥，正等待回覆，他希望林鄭月娥及港府可繼續維護中英聯合聲明及《基本法》。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171014/s00001/1507971252529\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171014%2Fs00001%2F1507971252529&d=qXMKaK5z5ZTd9Qcqkt%2FpdF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=ba2033db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171014%2Fs00001%2F1507971252529&h=2cdbf451\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171014/s00001/1507971252529</a>"},{"pid":"a2081373b452dedb7b54a630a51ea1953fa0dbb4","tid":435604,"uid":53687,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T12:12:47.000Z","msg":"林鄭：個別事件，不作評論"},{"pid":"bcf1c0570660cc97eb491e566ec6c3fb177c3bb0","tid":435604,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T12:13:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171014/s00001/04ddfd25bd0d58e65ce20cdb52c9b4c4.